text.text: I retract my previous rating, I thought they were straight in dealing with customers, I first called if a certain part was available, they said yes and the price was P3800 per piece. When I got there, the parts were not available daw, I tried to control my disappointment as I was about to schedule my car repair after I get the parts. Option was for them to order the parts for me that will take around 2 days, I said yes, they gave me the number of one of their salesman to text the parts that I wanted with the details of the car, I was surprised that when they texted back, the price already went up to P4800 per piece, at this point, I cancelled my supposed order, they can't argue that there was a price increase because I can get the same parts for the same price at another store.  I just went to them first as this was recommended to me by someone I know. Also, their salesman was a bit rude though not all of them naman, the one that I just talked to when I was there.
